::Lord ElderGrimlock::
   
  Elder hits a commlink after watching Kup and Elita's shuttle leave the area on the sensors.
   
  Elder: Lord Elder to shuttle port. Prepare two more shuttles for launch. We have to get moving with two missions immedietly.
   
  He turns to the rest.
   
  Elder: Alright so everyone on the rescue party assemble on this side of the room and be accounted for. Those on the Matrix Quest assemble over here.
   
  Elder stands on the side where the Matrix Quest crew should be.
   
  Grimlock stomps his way to the other side of the room.
   
  Grimlock: Me Grimlock help Hot Rod and wife!
